## OpenMeteo API Usage

This project uses the OpenMeteo API which is free for non-commercial use.
For commercial usage, please refer to [OpenMeteo Terms of Service](https://open-meteo.com/en/terms)
and [OpenMeteo Pricing](https://open-meteo.com/en/pricing).

OpenMeteo API:
- Free tier: Up to 10,000 API calls per day
- No API key required for non-commercial use
- Attribution appreciated but not required

